<paragraph id="0F5577993D31382EEE597E623830D577" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
MEXICO. Oaxaca, Tehuantepec, camino al Arroyo de Las Minas, 
<emphasis id="216850645E04B3287AE2B689AC8704BC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
R. Torres C. &amp; C. 
<normalizedToken id="6B6AA5E1670CE3F16A6B0D7A9C058AA2" originalValue="Martínez">Martinez</normalizedToken>
